Write a program code in the ST language for a PLC according to the IEC/EN 61131 standard, which counts the number of products (ProductCount) on a conveyor:

If the sensor (EntrySensor) detects a product, the ProductCount value increases by 1.
If the ExitSensor detects a product leaving, the ProductCount value decreases by 1.
The output ConveyorFull is activated when ProductCount reaches 50.







